         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Botanic Gardens Melbourne ¶ Decr 6. 1865 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor to inform you that, during the past night, a large quantity of exotic Ash Trees (50) have (by some person or persons unknown) been ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">65.12.06b</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Frederick Standish</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Unit 5, VPRS 1199 Chief Commissioner's inward correspondence, VA 724 Victoria Police, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Botanic Gardens Melbourne</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Decr 6. 1865</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have the honor to inform you that, during the past night, a large quantity of exotic Ash Trees (50) have (by some person or persons unknown) been wilfully destroyed in the Government House Reserve, close to the Observatory — As these trees are under my especial charge I have the honor to request your kind assistance in order that if possible the perpetrators of this malicious act may be brought to justice, and further destruction of like valuable public property be in future prevented —</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be Sir</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your most obdt Servt.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. Mueller</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Direct.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>bot Garden.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Captn Standish</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Chief Commissioner of Police<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Standish referred the matter to the officer in charge of detectives<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for inquiry and report.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>No account of the investigation has been found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
